## Gender Hints

<quick-reference name="gender-hints">
<title>Spot gender by ending</title>

| Gender    | Common Endings |
|-----------|----------------|
| Masculine | -ος, -ας, -ης, -ές |
| Feminine  | -α, -η, -ση, -ξη |
| Neuter    | -ο, -ι, -μα |

</quick-reference>

